 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Natural-cure:

    This Pokémon is cured of any 
  major status ailment when it 
  is switched out for another Pokémon.

  If this ability is acquired 
  during battle, the Pokémon is 
  cured upon leaving battle before 
  losing the temporary ability.

  Poison-point:

    Whenever a move makes contact 
  with this Pokémon, the move's 
  user has a 30% chance of being 
  poisoned.

  Leaf-guard:

    This Pokémon cannot be given 
  a major status ailment during 
  strong sunlight.

  This ability does not heal 
  prior status ailments. rest will 
  fail altogether with this ability 
  in effect. yawn will immediately 
  fail if used on this Pokémon 
  during strong sunlight, and an 
  already-used Yawn will fail if 
  the weather turns to strong sunlight 
  in the meantime.


